mainToolbarCustomizationProfile.Title: Select Profile
mainToolbarCustomizationProfile.ShortHel: Activates a comparison profile and updates the structure comparison with the compare statuses of this profile.
mainToolbarEditCustomization.Title: Edit Customization
mainToolbarEditCustomization.ShortHelp: Lets you create comparison profiles to customize the structure comparison.
mainToolbarEditCustomization.LongHelp: You can define your own matching rules for compare statuses, and display additional statuses based on properties comparison.
mainToolbarSwap.Title: Swap
mainToolbarSwap.ShortHelp: Swaps the left and right objects.
mainToolbarSwap.LongHelp: The comparison is recomputed, and all the tabs are updated.
mainToolbarDisplayViews.Title: Show or Hide Tabs
mainToolbarDisplayViews.ShortHelp: Lets you choose the tabs you want to display in Compare.
mainToolbarDisplayViews.LongHelp: Select the tabs you want to display, and clear the ones you want to hide.
mainToolbarRefresh.Title: Refresh
mainToolbarRefresh.ShortHelp: Refreshes the comparison results of the current objects.
mainToolbarExport.Title: Export Results
mainToolbarExport.ShortHelp: Exports the results of the structure and properties comparisons into a CSV file.
mainToolbarExport.LongHelp: The CSV file is saved into the browser's default download folder. The Export command is available when only two objects are being compared.
mainToolbarAdditionalMenu.Title: Additional Commands
externalRelations.Title: Compare Relations
externalRelations.ShortHelp: Compares and displays the attached documents and specification documents, or other available related objects.>
showDocs.Title: Compare Documents
showDocs.ShortHelp: Compares and displays attached and specification documents.
showOtherRels.Title: Compare Other Related Objects
showOtherRels.ShortHelp: Displays and compares other supported related objects.
closeAllObjects.Title: Close All Objects
closeAllObjects.ShortHelp: Removes all the compared objects from the widget, and returns to the home page.
mainToolbarRestoreLayout.Title: Restore Layout
mainToolbarRestoreLayout.ShortHelp: Restores the initial layout of the widget.
mainToolbarRestoreLayout.LongHelp: All your layout modifications are lost.
PreviousDifference.Title: Previous Difference
PreviousDifference.ShortHelp: Navigates to the previous difference in the tree or list.
NumberOfDifferences.Title: Number of Differences
NumberOfDifferences.ShortHelp: Indicates the number of non-identical rows.
NumberOfDifferences.LongHelp: Click to navigate to the first or last difference.
NextDifference.Title: Next Difference
NextDifference.ShortHelp: Navigates to the next difference in the tree or list.
FirstDifference.Title: First Difference
FirstDifference.ShortHelp: Navigates to the first difference in the tree or list.
LastDifference.Title: Last Difference
LastDifference.ShortHelp: Navigates to the last difference in the tree or list.
SM.Title: Identical
SM.ShortHelp: The objects on left and right are identical.
SM.LongHelp: Select this check box to display the rows with this status, or clear it to hide them.
LO.Title: Left-Only
LO.ShortHelp: No matching object has been found on the right structure.
LO.LongHelp: Select this check box to display the rows with this status, or clear it to hide them.
RO.Title: Right-Only
RO.ShortHelp: No matching object has been found on the left structure.
RO.LongHelp: Select this check box to display the rows with this status, or clear it to hide them.
REV.Title: Revision
REV.ShortHelp: The object has been replaced by another revision
REV.LongHelp: Select this check box to display the rows with this status, or clear it to hide them.
REPLACED.Title: Replaced
REPLACED.ShortHelp: The object has been replaced by an unrelated object that is neither a revision, a branch, nor a duplicate.
REPLACED.LongHelp: Select this check box to display the rows with this status, or clear it to hide them.
QUANTITY.Title: Quantity
QUANTITY.ShortHelp: The number of instances of the same object is different between the two structures.
QUANTITY.LongHelp: Select this check box to display the rows with this status, or clear it to hide them.
DUPLICATED.Title: Duplicate
DUPLICATED.ShortHelp: The object has been replaced by a duplicate, or an object derived from a duplicate.
DUPLICATED.LongHelp: Select this check box to display the rows with this status, or clear it to hide them.
BRANCHED.Title: Branch
BRANCHED.ShortHelp: The object has been replaced by a branch, or an object derived from a branch.
BRANCHED.LongHelp: Select this check box to display the rows with this status, or clear it to hide them.
DIFFERENT.Title: Different
DIFFERENT.ShortHelp: The two objects are unrelated but share common children (identical, revision, branch, duplicate or replaced).
DIFFERENT.LongHelp: Select this check box to display the rows with this status, or clear it to hide them.
UNRELATED.Title: Unrelated
UNRELATED.ShortHelp: The two roots or/and their descendants are unrelated.
UNRELATED.LongHelp: The descendants, if any, are indicated as left-only or right only. Select this check box to display the rows with this status, or clear it to hide them.
MOVED.Title: Position
MOVED.ShortHelp: Both objects are related (Identical, Revision, Branch, Duplicate, Different) but the position is different.
MOVED.LongHelp: Select this check box to display the rows with this status, or clear it to hide them.
REFMODIFIED.Title: Modified Reference
REFMODIFIED.ShortHelp: Both objects are related (Identical, Revision, Branch, Duplicate, Different) but modifications have been done.
REFMODIFIED.LongHelp: Select this check box to display the rows with this status, or clear it to hide them.
INSTMODIFIED.Title: Modified Instance
INSTMODIFIED.ShortHelp: Both objects are related (Identical, Revision, Branch, Duplicate, Different) but modifications have been done.
INSTMODIFIED.LongHelp: Select this check box to display the rows with this status, or clear it to hide them.
CHILDMODIFIED.Title: Modified Child
CHILDMODIFIED.ShortHelp: Both objects are related (Identical, Revision, Branch, Duplicate, Different) but modifications have been done to a child.
CHILDMODIFIED.LongHelp: Select this check box to display the rows with this status, or clear it to hide them.
chooseStatusToDisplay.Title: Select Statuses to Display
chooseStatusToDisplay.ShortHelp: Lets you choose the statuses you want to use in the structure comparison.
chooseStatusToDisplay.LongHelp: Select the statuses you want to use, and clear the other ones. If you clear a status, the objects are displayed in the structure comparison, but are considered as identical.
chooseTreeExpansion.Title: Select Expansion Level of Tree
ExpandAll.Title: Expand All
ExpandAll.ShortHelp: Expands all the children of the selected object.
ExpandNLevels.Title: Expand N Levels
ExpandNLevels.ShortHelp: Expands the tree up to the number of levels you specify.
CollapseAll.Title: Collapse All
CollapseAll.ShortHelp: Collapses all the children of the selected object.
chooseTreeOrListView.Title: View Selector
StructureView.Title: Tree View
StructureView.ShortHelp: Displays the structure comparison in a parent-child view.
StructureView.LongHelp: This view provides information about the position of individual instances. It does not provide information about the quantity of instances of the same objects
ListView.Title: List View
ListView.ShortHelp: Displays the structure comparison as a list of objects
ListView.LongHelp: This view provides information about the quantity of instances of the same objects. It does not provide information about the position of individual instances.
attrShowDiffOnly.Title: Show Differences Only
attrShowDiffOnly.ShortHelp: Displays only the properties that are different between the two objects, and hide identical properties
selectPropertiesToDisplay.Title: Select Properties to Display
selectPropertiesToDisplay.ShortHelp: Lets you choose the properties displayed in the Properties tab.
selectPropertiesToDisplay.LongHelp: Select the properties you want to display, and clear the ones you want to hide.
ProfilesTitleTooltips.Title: Select Profile
ProfilesTitleTooltips.ShortHelp: Select the comparison profile that you want to modify, duplicate, or delete.
ProfilesTitleTooltips.LongHelp: If a profile is being modified when you select it, you are asked to save or discard those modifications before changing to this profile.
DuplicateProfileTooltips.Title: Duplicate Profile
DuplicateProfileTooltips.ShortHelp: Creates a copy of the selected comparison profile to create a new one.
DuplicateProfileTooltips.LongHelp: Matching rules and additional statuses are also copied. You can modify or remove them, and add new ones.
DeleteProfileTooltips.Title: Delete Profile
DeleteProfileTooltips.ShortHelp: Permanently deletes the selected comparison profile.
DeleteProfileTooltips.LongHelp: You must confirm or cancel the deletion.
ObjectTypesTooltips.Title: Object Types
ObjectTypesTooltips.ShortHelp: Lists the object types the selected comparison profile applies to.
InterfacesTooltips.Title: Extensions
InterfacesTooltips.ShortHelp: Lists the extension attributes available for use in custom comparison.
RolesTooltips.Title: Roles
RolesTooltips.ShortHelp: Defines the roles involved with this customization.
AllowCustomMatchingRulesTooltips.Title: Allow Custom Matching Rules
AllowCustomMatchingRulesTooltips.ShortHe: Allows the creation of compare statuses with custom matching rules in the comparison profile.
RuleOrderTooltips.Title: Matching Rule Order
RuleOrderTooltips.ShortHelp: The priority of the matching rules is based on the order of the rows in this table.
MatchingRuleTooltips.Title: Define Matching Rules
MatchingRuleTooltips.ShortHelp: Defines the properties that you want to compare for each compare status used in this profile, in order of priority.
MatchingRuleTooltips.LongHelp: Compare statuses that you define in this section are applied to objects if all the listed properties are similar for the object in both structures.
UseDefaultMatchingRulesTooltips.Title: Use Default Rules
UseDefaultMatchingRulesTooltips.ShortHel: Use default matching rules when comparing objects.
UseCustomMatchingRulesTooltips.Title: Use Custom Rules
UseCustomMatchingRulesTooltips.ShortHelp: Use the custom matching rules when comparing objects.
AddMatchingRuleTooltips.Title: Add Matching Rule
AddMatchingRuleTooltips.ShortHelp: Creates a matching rule for compared objects, and an associated compare status.
AddMatchingRuleTooltips.LongHelp: The compare status is added at the end of the table. You can reorder compare statuses later.
AllowUserToOverrideTooltips.Title: Allow User to Override Matching Rules
AllowUserToOverrideTooltips.ShortHelp: Defines whether or not this profile allows user to override the matching rules
AdditionalStatusTooltips.Title: Define Additional Statuses
AdditionalStatusTooltips.ShortHelp: Defines the properties that you want to compare for each additional compare status used in this profile.
AdditionalStatusTooltips.LongHelp:
These statuses are displayed next to regular compare statuses defined in the Matching Rules section if any of the properties that you listed for those statuses is different between the object in the left structure and the object in the right structure.

The Properties status applies to the properties of the object (reference), while the Instance status applies to the properties of the object's instance in the structure.
AddAdditionalStatusTooltips.Title: Add Additional Status
AddAdditionalStatusTooltips.ShortHelp: Adds an additional status rule to this profile.
AddAdditionalStatusTooltips.LongHelp: Add an empty additional status rule at the end of the table. The fields outlined in red are required and must be filled in.
SaveCustomizationTooltips.Title: Save Profile
SaveCustomizationTooltips.ShortHelp: Saves your modifications, and returns to the previous page.
CancelCustomizationTooltips.Title: Cancel
CancelCustomizationTooltips.ShortHelp: Cancels your modifications, and returns to the previous page.
CancelCustomizationTooltips.LongHelp: If there are profile modifications in process when you cancel, your changes are discarded.
